TITLE      Polarization effects in the C-12(3He,pp) reaction
           at 33 MeV
AUTHOR     (O.Karban,L.Potvin,I.M.Turkiewicz)
INSTITUTE  (2UK BIR,3POLWWA)
REFERENCE  (J,NP/A,460,529,1986)
           #doi:10.1016/0375-9474(86)90427-6
FACILITY   (CYCLO,2UK BIR)
COMMENT    In the article double differential cross sections are
           presented as the angular distribution of helium-2.
           He-2 does not have a bound state and is not
           established as a short-lived state.
